{"tid":1718139,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[浸大守城] 小心重蹈佔領時嘅覆轍","createTime":"2019-11-13T18:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T11:58:18.000Z","uid":315038,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7173e0f85c49699da76bccf29c83ab36becd843b","tid":1718139,"uid":315038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:50:39.000Z","msg":"唔係批評，只係提醒浸大人開始要諗定<br />\n以前兩傘79係因為佔路漸漸令民意逆轉而潰散<br />\n而家浸大個防守陣佔咗一段聯合道同窩打老道，三幾日問題唔大(守得到嘅話)<br />\n但浸大同中大唔一樣，中大自成一角，唔太會影響其他區嘅人<br />\n所以，時間一長肯定會影響民情<br />\n(唔好同我話人一早歸晒邊，民意唔會逆轉。馬鞍山火人已經話畀你知世事冇絕對)<br />\n咁所以，我諗你地要諗定點變陣 (e.g. 改防守設計，改守舊校，守其他大學，etc)<br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔割<br />\n一定要嬴<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"fe93bcd5d419f01c71915036441c06a6ee334a33","tid":1718139,"uid":194399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:00:12.000Z","msg":"民意其實好重要, 大家盡量唔好忽視<br />\n___________________________________<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>「請廣傳」香港黑警濫權資料庫 (中英日語）</ins></span></strong><br />\n依個網手足籌劃左好一段時間, 包含大量核彈, 請各位出分力廣傳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港警察濫權實錄資料庫<br />\nH.K. Police Violence Database<br />\n香港警察暴行の事件簿</span><br />\n中文<br />\n<a href=\"http://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline%2F&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZNTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=ff6a12d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/</a><br />\nEng<br />\n<a href=\"http://tl.hkrev.info/en/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fen%2Fpolice-timeline%2F&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZNTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=e59a93eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tl.hkrev.info/en/police-timeline/</a><br />\n日文<br />\n<a href=\"http://tl.hkrev.info/ja/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fja%2Fpolice-timeline&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZNTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=97bbd05b\" data-auto-l